snippet.title: Neofeud Trailer (Official)
snippet.description:
Neofeud is a dystopic sci-fi / cyberpunk adventure game.   Get it here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/673850/Neofeud/

You can also get it on Itch.io: https://silverspook.itch.io/neofeud

(Warning: Trailer and game contains imagery that may affect players with photosensitive epilepsy.)
